Hadoop API

1. Common -
      File system -->org.apache.hadoop.fs
      IO -->org.apache.hadoop.io
      Util-->org.apache.hadoop.util
      
2. Mapreduce -  org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce
      Mapper --> org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Mapper
      Reducer --> org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Reducer
      Partitioner --> org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Partitioner
3. Yarn


InputFormat-->FileInputFormat-->TextInputFormat

OutputFormat-->FileOutputFormat-->TextOutputFormat

Mapper output-->Shuffle (Partitioning, Grouping)-->Sort-->Reducer

Partitioning-->depends on number of reducer-->Default hash partition--> hash key % (mod functin) no.of reducer

